<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拿著捕蟲網<delay20 />追著蟲跑，<delay20 />
會讓我想起小時候啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抓到稀奇蟲子時的<delay20 />
那種心情<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使變成大人，也忘記不了咧，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得今天能釣到大傢伙。<delay frames="40" />
為了隨時都能對付牠們，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我才會隨身帶著釣竿啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到我澆水覺得很意外嗎！？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過啊，<delay20 />需要我澆水的<delay20 />
可不只有花喔？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是蔬菜啊、大頭菜啊，<delay20 />
也都需要喝水的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會種出一片最棒的菜園。你等著瞧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay20 />對傘可是很講究的。<delay frames="40" />
還會依當天心情換傘咧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然有些傘只會在這種天氣撐，<delay20 />
所以少有露面機會，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我可是會經常在家鑑賞的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>